Meet Spiro!  Powerhouse, work horse, spitfire, social butterfly and all around genuinely sweet human with a passion for helping others.  With years of experience as an award winning Realtor, Spiro set the stage for mortgage greatness well before he picked up his first calculator.  As one of the most successful realtors in their brokerage hitting the Millionaire Club designation with ease within his first year in the business, he is definitely not one to shy away from a challenge. 

His industry knowledge as a successful agent turned mortgage guru gives him an insight like no other into the psychology of real estate enabling him to best serve our client base.  Beyond this, he is a Social media Guru (emphasis on the social,) marketing master and all around beast of a workhorse.  Nothing can stop Spiro!  Yes, he is small yet mighty! 

I am so blessed to have this beautiful human representing the brand that is Team Ubaldo and look forward to watching him move mountains, change lives and eventually pay it forward!  Congratulations @heracles_189 welcome to the team!

Happy Mortgage Monday Y’all 😃 

Just wanted to share finally 😅 our experience and what we are doing in the current market. We never give advice that we do not take ourselves 🏡
We purchased a home in Pennsylvania this year and next year our goal is another home in another state! 🎉

We know posts on loan products can be a little boring but we post them to educate our friends, family & clients who are  also family to us so that it gives you the knowledge and confidence to face this market with a clearer mind. We are here to answer questions and educate. 

We love sharing knowledge and making sure you feel the best when making this huge decision in your lives. 

We are always here for all of you and want you to feel comfortable coming to us and asking them so that we can make it a great experience without that anxiety. Plus you get our smiling faces 😅❤️ 

Also our settlement service company was the absolute best! Shonna and her team made our experience so incredibly amazing and if you are purchasing a home in PA I highly recommend you use their services! Thank you Shonna ❤️
